!begin_node (!kw [use_auto_subsubsubsubtocs])
!html_name cmd_use_auto_subsubsubsubtocs

Automatically create tables of contents in paragraphs.

!begin_xlist [(!TYPEPOSITION)]

!item [(!TYPEPOSITION)] (!SWITCH), (!PREAMBLE)

!item [(!SYNTAX)] (!T)!/use_auto_subsubsubsubtocs [(!FORMAT)](!t)

!item [(!DESCRIPTION)]
Tells UDO to use the (!KW [subsubsubsubtoc]) command automatically in every
paragraph. The example shows how to use them inside the hypertext
formats.

!item [(!EXISTSSINCE)] Release~5 Patchlevel~16

!item [(!SEEALSO)]
(!KW [subsubsubsubtoc]), (!KW [ignore_subsubsubsubtoc]), (!link [Tables of contents] [Tables of contents])

!end_xlist

(!EXAMPLE)
(!EXAMPLE_BEGIN)
!begin_verbatim
!use_auto_subsubsubsubtocs [html,pch,stg,win]
!end_verbatim
(!EXAMPLE_END)

!end_node
